metadata.name: 07SC-18Mountains-16Sea-16Sea-55Sky-55Sky-19Trees-65Trees
metadata.description:
07SC-18Mountains-16Sea-16Sea-55Sky-55Sky-19Trees-65Trees is a unique artwork from Land Sea and Sky by Jennifer and Kevin McCoy, a collection of enigmatic landscape collages built by combining compositional forms based on iconic 20th-century landscape photography with AI-generated imagery of the American countryside. 

Land Sea and Sky was commissioned by Artwrld.
